},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":27}],"windowDisplayName":"토우코","body":"아니아니, 그러면 내가 더 장난 아니잖아!\n내가 퍼포먼스 할 때마다 무조건 공연장이 달아올랐는데!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":27,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":27,"voiceId":"BSP-MS-ep1-046","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":28}],"windowDisplayName":"나나미","body":"확실히, 토~코 짱이 점프하면\n어느새 관객도 점프하게 됐지~","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":28,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":28,"voiceId":"BSP-MS-ep1-047","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":27}],"windowDisplayName":"토우코","body":"그치~? 역시 나는 천재라니까~!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":27,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":27,"voiceId":"BSP-MS-ep1-048","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":29}],"windowDisplayName":"츠쿠시","body":"그, 그러면 나도 지금까지 중에 제일 잘 쳤는데.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":29,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":29,"voiceId":"BSP-MS-ep1-049","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":29}],"windo